    <h1>Video Completion Rate</h1>
    <p class="description">The percentage of video plays that reach the end. A primary <strong>algorithmic quality signal</strong> on TikTok, Reels, Shorts, and YouTube — and the metric that determines how widely a video gets distributed.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
